<MELItem itemNbr="29-11-01" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-29-11-01.1.2-29-11-01">
<Title>Engine Driven Pumps (EDP) Depressurization Function</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="2" nbrRequired="1" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>One may be inoperative deactivated.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Deactivate inoperative engine driven pump depressurization function (AMM DDG 29-11-01).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>For left EDP depressurization function inoperative, using a flight deck multi-function display only, open the EDP DEPRESS-L circuit breaker and lock with an INOP tag.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>For right EDP depressurization function inoperative, using a flight deck multi-function display only, open the EDP DEPRESS-R circuit breaker and lock with an INOP tag.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
</DispatchItems>